high_descs: Walk towards the counter next to the stove
Grab a knife from the counter
Walk with the knife towards the counter next to the stools
Slice the apple on the counter
Walk with the knife towards the microwave
Put the knife in the microwave
Walk towards the counter
Take a slice of the apple
Walk with the slice of the apple
Put the slice of apple inside the microwave and cook it
Walk to the right towards the sink
Set the slice of apple in the sink
anns.task_desc: Slice the apple, put knife slice of apple in the microwave, set slice of apple in sink

high_descs: Turn left and move toward the silver dishwasher, then turn right and move to counter between the range and the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife between the salt shaker and the black toaster on the counter.
Turn right and move toward the gray door, then turn right and move to the black stools in the corner of the room next to the counter.
Use the knife to slice the apple next to the red credit card on the counter.
Turn right and move forward toward the blue trash bin then turn left and move to the red microwave to the left of the dishwasher.
Open the microwave and place the knife on the plate, then close the microwave.
Turn right and move towards the range then turn right and move toward the gray door, then turn right and move to the black stools next to the counter.
Pick up one apple slice from the sliced apple next to the red credit card and gray bowl.
Turn right and move forward toward the blue trash bin then turn left and move to the red microwave to the left of the dishwasher.

Place the apple slice to the rear of the knife on the plate in the microwave, microwave the apple slice, open the microwave door, pick up the apple slice from the plate, then close the microwave door.
Turn to the right and move toward the range then turn to the left and face the sink.
Place the apple slice in front of the gray plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple slice in the sink.

high_descs: Go straight and to the left to the counter to the left of the fridge.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn right, go to the door, turn right, go between the window and the counter, face the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into pieces.
Go around the counter to the right and go to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around, go back to the area between the window and the counter and face the counter.
Take a piece of apple from the counter.
Go around the counter to the right and go to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave, take the apple from the microwave.
Turn right, go to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple in a sink.
